      <abstract>
        <p>Paula Beer, director of account management at New York office of Mad Dogs and Englishmen, is named general manager of new San Francisco office; James Maxwell, partner and chief executive of Ketchum London, is named to new additional post of managing director for European operations (S)</p>
      </abstract>
