    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* Paula Beer, director of account management at the New York office of Mad Dogs and Englishmen, was named general manager of a new San Francisco office.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>* Paula Beer, director of account management at the New York office of Mad Dogs and Englishmen, was named general manager of a new San Francisco office.</p>
        <p>* James Maxwell, partner and chief executive at Ketchum London, part of the Ketchum unit of the Omnicom Group, was named to the new additional post of managing director for European operations.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
